@module wiringRender  src=wiringRender.lua  loc=2712  sha=76f1f9c  mode=chunk
@deps cm, cmgr, chrome, gui, modalHost, wv

# Invariants & contracts
  @invariant  render + input only — holds wv only, never wm/rm; all queries/mutations go through wv.
  @invariant  renderer owns every pixel — geometry, port layout, hit-tests. See docs/wiringPage.md
  @invariant  wires draw as a pre-pass before nodes — centre-to-centre lines occluded by the bodies; parallel wires in one unordered pair are offset perpendicularly, MIDI sorted to the right.
  @invariant  port rows are top/bottom only. See docs/wiringPage.md § The port band.
  @invariant  key bindings + wiring-scope command bodies live here; coord pushes scope on activation.
  @contract  wiringPage (the controller) owns the stack (rm/wm/wv) and hands this renderer wv only

# Shapes
  @shape  returns { slots, handle, bandRect, list, hoverRect, side, popup } (all canvas-local).

